BULLET::::- Colin C. Haley. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.internetnews.com/infra/article.php/3494291"&gt;SBC Closes in on Video Strategy&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Ainternetnews.com"&gt;internetnews.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 31, 2005
