BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.worldscreen.com/newscurrent.php%3Ffilename%3DHBO331.htm"&gt;HBO Rolls Out More Channels in Asia&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWorld%20Screen%20News"&gt;World Screen News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, March 31, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cinemaxasia.com/about/milestones.jsp%3FcurCountry%3D65"&gt;The history of HBO Asia&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACinemax"&gt;Cinemax&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,

</ul>


