BULLET::::- Australian Broadcasting Corporation. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200504/s1337279.htm"&gt;Teams maintain whale rescue efforts&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAustralian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation"&gt;Australian Broadcasting Corporation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 4, 2005

