BULLET::::- Ken Warren. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.canada.com/ottawa/ottawacitizen/news/sports/story.html%3Fid%3Da9267c36-4cb7-441b-8d32-0d34fe47b873"&gt;Former players describe 'Professor' as real character, perfectionist&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Ottawa%20Citizen"&gt;The Ottawa Citizen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 4, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cfl.ca/index.php%3Fmodule%3Dnewser%26amp%3Bfunc%3Ddisplay%26amp%3Bnid%3D5128"&gt;CFL legend Frank Clair passes&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACanadian%20Football%20League"&gt;Canadian Football League&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 4, 2005

