BULLET::::- Katie Zezima. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/04/05/national/05bigdig.html%3Fex%3D1113364800%26amp%3Ben%3De0951e9afd2c0b2d%26amp%3Bei%3D5070"&gt;U.S. declares Boston's Big Dig safe for motorists&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20New%20York%20Times"&gt;The New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 5, 2005

