BULLET::::- National Conference 2005. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.senterpartiet.no/landsmote_2005/"&gt;The official webpages&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACentre_Party_%28Norway%29"&gt;Centre_Party_(Norway)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 5, 2005

