BULLET::::- Richard Luscombe. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.scotsman.com/international.cfm%3Fid%3D362562005"&gt;US woman boxer dies in chilling echo of Oscar film&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AScotsman.com"&gt;Scotsman.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 6, 2005
