BULLET::::- Paul Richter. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/la-040505passports_lat%2C0%2C698287.story%3Fcoll%3Dla-home-headlines"&gt;New Rules Tighten U.S. Passport Requirements&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AL.A.%20Times"&gt;L.A. Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 5, 2005
