BULLET::::- John Foley. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.informationweek.com/story/showArticle.jhtml%3FarticleID%3D160403344"&gt;Business Adoption Of Windows XP SP2 Still Low, Survey F&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AInformation%20Week"&gt;Information Week&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 4, 2005

