BULLET::::- Christopher Bowe in New York. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.ft.com/cms/s/370ca734-a790-11d9-9744-00000e2511c8.html"&gt;Pfizer forced to swallow bitter pill&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFinancial%20Times%20%28London%29"&gt;Financial Times (London)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 7, 2005 19:25 UTC

