BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.army.mil/medalofhonor/citation/printable.html"&gt;Battlescape narrative&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUS%20Army"&gt;US Army&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 4, 2005

</ul>


