BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.co.uk/News/newsArticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DentertainmentNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2005-04-08T184837Z_01_CAS867561_RTRUKOC_0_MEDIA-MEANFIDDLER.xml"&gt;Mean Fiddler agrees takeover&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 8, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//breakingnews.iol.ie/news/story.asp%3Fj%3D139281798%26amp%3Bp%3Dy39z8z5x4"&gt;Music promoter awaits investor takeover&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AIreland%20Online"&gt;Ireland Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 8, 2005
