BULLET::::- Ingrid Marson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.zdnet.co.uk/internet/0%2C39020369%2C39194162%2C00.htm"&gt;Wikipedia planning a DVD version&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AZD%20Net%20UK"&gt;ZD Net UK&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 07, 2005, 17:05 BST
