BULLET::::- Associated Press-- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2005/04/09/politics/09stamps.html"&gt;Stamps may cost 39 cents&lt;/a&gt;. ♡❤The New York Times♡❤ April 9, 2005

