BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4429307.stm"&gt;SA apartheid party set to disband&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News%20World%20Edition"&gt;BBC News World Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/sf.html%23Govt"&gt;The World Factbook: South Africa&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACIA"&gt;CIA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, updated on February 10, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.uneca.org/temp2/Library/Southern"&gt;Africa Monitor September 2004.pdf SA: Too Close For Comfort?&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAfrica%20Monitor%3A%20Souther%20Africa%2C%20Vol%209%2C%20No%209%2C%20pp.%202%2C%204"&gt;Africa Monitor: Souther Africa, Vol 9, No 9, pp. 2, 4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 2004
