BULLET::::- Sabine Siebold. "&lt;a href="http%3A//xtramsn.co.nz/entertainment/0%2C%2C12254-4287721%2C00.html"&gt;Cannibal Launches Rival Appeal&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEntertainment%3A%20News%20%26amp%3B%20Gossip%3A"&gt;Entertainment: News &amp; Gossip:&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 14, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.cbc.ca/cp/world/050413/w041334.html"&gt;Germany-Cannibal-Trial&lt;/a&gt; Canadian Broadcasting Co April 13, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.smh.com.au/news/World/German-court-reviews-conviction-of-human-butcher/2005/04/13/1113251686028.html%3Foneclick%3Dtrue"&gt;German court reviews conviction of 'human butcher'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASydney%20Morning%20Herald%20%28Aus%29"&gt;Sydney Morning Herald (Aus)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 14, 2005

</ul>


