BULLET::::- Tania Branigan. "&lt;a href="http%3A//politics.guardian.co.uk/election/story/0%2C15803%2C1459032%2C00.html%3Fgusrc%3Drss"&gt;Kennedy eager to fight Labour on home turf&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Guardian"&gt;The Guardian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 14
