BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.usatoday.com/news/offbeat/2005-04-14-bugs_x.htm"&gt;Bush gets a bug of his own&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 14, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DoddlyEnoughNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D8180310"&gt;Oddly Enough: Bush, Cheney, Rumsfeld share beetles honor&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 14, 2005

