BULLET::::- FOX News' Jane Roh and Adam Housley and The Associated Press contributed to this report.. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C153607%2C00.html"&gt;Mark Hacking Pleads Guilty to Murder&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFOXNews.com"&gt;FOXNews.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 15, 2005
