<doc id="8258" url="https://en.wikinews.org/wiki?curid=8258" title="Over a quarter of a billion camera phones sold in 2004">
<h1>Over a quarter of a billion camera phones sold in 2004</h1>
&lt;strong class="published"&gt;&lt;span id="publishDate" class="value-title" title=""&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="Z3988" style="display:none" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rfr_id=rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:User%3ADendodge&amp;rft_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:&amp;rft.atitle=Over%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20billion%20camera%20phones%20sold%20in%202004&amp;rft.jtitle=Wikinews&amp;rft.date=&amp;rft.aucorp=Wikinews+contributors&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.rights=CC-BY+2.5&amp;rft.identifier=&amp;rft.artnum="&gt; &lt;/span&gt; 

New research revealed earlier this week indicates that some 257m &lt;a href="w%3Acamera%20phones"&gt;camera phones&lt;/a&gt; were shipped worldwide in 2004. The survey carried out by Strategy Analytics showed that camera phone sales have soared over 200% from 84m in 2003 to the 257m last year.

The huge surge in sales means that camera phone sales now outnumber &lt;a href="w%3Adigital%20camera"&gt;digital camera&lt;/a&gt; sales four to one. The mobile phone market ended the year as follows:

<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="w%3ANokia"&gt;Nokia&lt;/a&gt; - 18 percent market share,
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="w%3AMotorola"&gt;Motorola&lt;/a&gt; - 17 percent,
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="w%3ASamsung"&gt;Samsung&lt;/a&gt; - 13 percent,
BULLET::::- Others - 52.1 percent.

</ul>
Despite the astonishing growth last year, the survey predicts a future increase to more than 350 million camera phones sales this year.

<h2>Sources</h2>

<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dmeurope.com/default.asp%3FArticleID%3D7336"&gt;257m camera phones shipped worldwide in 2004&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADigital%20Media%20Europe"&gt;Digital Media Europe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 15, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.enn.ie/news.html%3Fcode%3D9599267"&gt;Camera phone sales gain momentum&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AElectricnews.net"&gt;Electricnews.net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 15, 2005
