BULLET::::- Frank Ahrens. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A57656-2005Apr15.html"&gt;FDA Orders Levitra Ad Off the Air&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashingtonpost.com"&gt;Washingtonpost.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 16, 2005
BULLET::::- Carla Mozee. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.marketwatch.com/news/story.asp%3Fguid%3D%257B5BA58EF2-0F51-4C4C-A95B-0953317769EB%257D%26amp%3Bsiteid%3Dmktw"&gt;FDA orders Bayer, Glaxo to pull Levitra TV ad&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMarketWatch%20%28Pharmaceuticals%29"&gt;MarketWatch (Pharmaceuticals)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 16, 2005

