BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.bloomberg.com/apps/news%3Fpid%3D10000102%26amp%3Bsid%3DaLjkdiSZoMac%26amp%3Brefer%3Duk"&gt;Littlewoods to Cut 3,200 Jobs; Sell 33 Index Shops&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABloomberg"&gt;Bloomberg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 17, 2005
