BULLET::::- ♡❤♡Subs Not Used:♡❤♡ Carroll, Silvestre.
BULLET::::- ♡❤♡Booked:♡❤♡ Ronaldo, Brown, Heinze.
BULLET::::- ♡❤♡Goals:♡❤♡ van Nistelrooy 19, Scholes 45, van Nistelrooy 58, Ronaldo 76.

</ul>
